---
description: Daily GitHub sync at session start or after time away
alwaysApply: false
---
Follow `.claude/skills/github-sync/SKILL.md` at session start or after time away, once per
calendar day — check `notes/github-sync/YYYY-MM-DD.md` for today's date first. Claude Code's
version is driven by a `SessionStart` hook (`.claude/settings.json`); Cursor has no hook system at
all (`docs/agent/workflow-map.md` §5), so this rule is best-effort, not a guaranteed daily trigger.
